607
00:42:34,171 --> 00:42:37,071
- Then leave him in the garden. 
- I'll take him out later.

608
00:42:37,171 --> 00:42:41,341
I have to have a deep conversation with him at the moment.

609
00:42:52,371 --> 00:42:54,071
All of you haven't forgotten, right?

610
00:42:54,171 --> 00:42:57,371
Article 1, Section 1 of your contract, duty of confidentiality.

611
00:43:02,741 --> 00:43:03,741
All right.

612
00:43:05,071 --> 00:43:10,441
This is like a sacred ground which no one can enter without permission.

613
00:43:11,441 --> 00:43:13,871
No one can bother us...

