615
00:43:20,471 --> 00:43:21,471
Come out.

616
00:43:25,271 --> 00:43:27,501
It's all right. Come out.

617
00:43:31,271 --> 00:43:32,271
Hey.

618
00:43:32,971 --> 00:43:34,601
Tell me the truth.

619
00:43:35,971 --> 00:43:38,171
You're just a dog, aren't you?

