622
00:44:00,141 --> 00:44:04,141
Yoo Jin Oh, you scum!

623
00:44:04,271 --> 00:44:08,341
Because of that jerk, I had to care for the dog.

624
00:44:09,141 --> 00:44:11,871
- Once you show up, I'll... 
- Stop it.

625
00:44:12,571 --> 00:44:16,401
This is why celebrities are scared of their fans turning on them.

626
00:44:16,441 --> 00:44:19,441
Everything about you bothers me now.

627
00:44:22,771 --> 00:44:24,071
Mr. Baek.

