I was on my way there. You didn't have to come out.

629
00:44:26,271 --> 00:44:28,901
Would it be okay to move it to 6pm?

630
00:44:29,371 --> 00:44:31,771
Well, sure. I'll be there on time.

631
00:44:35,171 --> 00:44:36,171
Gosh!

