00:45:29,241 --> 00:45:33,241
They say your talent would be taken away if you don't make it through.

646
00:45:33,271 --> 00:45:34,471
That novel...

647
00:45:35,371 --> 00:45:37,371
I really hope you complete it.

648
00:45:38,341 --> 00:45:39,971
It doesn't matter when.

649
00:45:44,471 --> 00:45:45,501
I...

