695
00:48:54,505 --> 00:48:55,805
That novel...

696
00:48:56,405 --> 00:48:58,505
I really hope you complete it.

697
00:48:59,735 --> 00:49:01,705
It doesn't matter when.

698
00:49:03,305 --> 00:49:06,705
