00:54:28,275 --> 00:54:31,335
You applied for Se Ju's camp, didn't you?

761
00:54:32,005 --> 00:54:34,805
Well, that's right.

762
00:54:35,835 --> 00:54:37,575
Anyway, think about it and call me.

