791
00:57:03,035 --> 00:57:04,805
What are you doing right now?

792
00:57:05,705 --> 00:57:09,735
I told you. I don't want to lose anything to you anymore.

793
00:57:14,405 --> 00:57:16,205
Hello?

794
00:57:16,935 --> 00:57:18,235
Guys.

795
00:57:21,075 --> 00:57:22,275
Guys.

796
00:57:24,635 --> 00:57:25,735
Let's go.

797
00:58:27,205 --> 00:58:30,205
(Chicago Typewriter)

798
00:58:30,205 --> 00:58:31,975
