805
00:58:45,205 --> 00:58:47,605
Do you want to go to the suburb with me?

806
00:58:47,605 --> 00:58:49,235
I know a quiet and an atmospheric cafe.

807
00:58:49,235 --> 00:58:50,475
Should I go and bite him?

808
00:58:50,805 --> 00:58:53,035
- I can see my past life. 
- Do you know?

809
00:58:53,405 --> 00:58:55,005
Do you know who Ryu Su Hyeon is?
